{"tid":1625060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係淺草寺幫香港求左之簽","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:26:12.000Z","uid":21976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9138f7827ec1edcf648d6d9bcec37c247fceb55f","tid":1625060,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPnOO4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPnOO4m.png&h=7d5ab894&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFxSwhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFxSwhP.png&h=a565e102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人識完全解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ded1e26aecc2b8c2bb9faeaa4d8b914a3db9d11","tid":1625060,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自膠"},{"pid":"6aa2cbde4e9ecde005c7c4b3f5e66ef9c1f9d7ce","tid":1625060,"uid":319806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"中間英文個part唔係解釋嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb1e41822b61b3188a6a009c58988f3b489d5f9","tid":1625060,"uid":143116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"有朋友喺fb譯咗，幫佢copy過來<br />\n<br />\n淺草寺解籤<br />\n利申：唔好諗住岩哂 但意思應該差唔多<br />\n利申2: 無連登ac, 有既話可以轉告一下<br />\n<br />\n香港人（應該指前線，甚至係示威者同文宣等）博既係好努力既<br />\n亦都比人（應該指其他人，eg.打工仔、街坊等）睇到咁樣做既目的<br />\n<br />\n只不過呢...大家係依個階段嚟講都仲未成熟<br />\n而依個「未成熟」亦可以話係<br />\n未能完全成功既原因<br />\n依方面需要改善下<br />\n<br />\n文宣方面要加強<br />\n要做好文宣<br />\n將想要傳達既訊息<br />\n清清楚楚咁傳開去<br />\n<br />\n甚至乎要比人理解到<br />\n點解要咁做<br />\n我地想要啲乜野<br />\n我地點樣幫香港<br />\n我地點樣幫香港人<br />\n如果我地唔咁做會點樣<br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n而且要好清楚<br />\n唔係單純<br />\n「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n而係要解釋<br />\n<br />\n最後會向成功發展<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係<br />\n目的大家睇到<br />\n行動未夠成熟<br />\n文宣要加強同更加正中紅心<br />\n解釋清楚我地既目的、動機等等<br />\n會成功既"},{"pid":"0552aa1cf8907549520a86fef101cc623daf11ed","tid":1625060,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"睇英文睇得出要時間, 要慢慢黎"}]}